                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-23-off126 t17870221-23-cd127"></join> last, one leather pormanteau, value 5 s. six linen shirts, value 6 s. six linen crayats, value 3 s. six handkerchiefs; value 3 s. one pair of silk breeches, value 5 s. and six pair of thread stockings, value 6 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870221-23-victim332" type="victimName">
